      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/bd5aa8aa-1931-11e4-bd79-5254006e85c2).  Ran 16 tests.  No failures.",
